{"tid":1891542,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"南韓今日再爆142單新型肺炎，大爆法，香港絕要對南韓旅客實施隔離14天","createTime":"2020-02-22T02:24:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-22T03:52:30.000Z","uid":52978,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"830d9c790cadf633027b5643c81fb2e5e479043a","tid":1891542,"uid":52978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T02:24:14.000Z","msg":"韓國新型冠狀病毒疫情持續爆發，韓聯社今日（22日）早上報道，當地新增142宗確診個案，累計346宗。<br />\n<br />\n報道稱，新增的142宗病例中，有131宗發生在大邱和慶尚北道地區，其中38宗與大邱的新天地耶穌教會有關，另有92宗與發生醫院內集體感染的淸道大南醫院有關。<br />\n韓國第4大城市大邱是疫情重災區，當地的新天地耶穌教會有一名61歲女信徒，於本月18日確診，她被認為是感染多人的「超級傳播者」。不過外界懷疑該教會內另有隱形的「超級傳播者」。而韓國政府為遏止疫情，昨日宣布大邱市、慶尚北道清道郡為「特別管理地域」，全力提供控疫所需的人力物力。"},{"pid":"bdfc45cf5136169bcf8ecb6a984ca13166470167","tid":1891542,"uid":52978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T02:26:12.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6feee0cbb875328a7676ec011131f62b29aa4ffc","tid":1891542,"uid":52978,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T02:27:08.000Z","msg":"南韓咁爆法，hk要封埋佢，唔係又多個源頭區"},{"pid":"7ca090115d52e75361a90fbc08babc9f85940a02","tid":1891542,"uid":281516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T02:27:13.000Z","msg":"商機無限之。醫護集體大移民<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fckKuS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fckKuS</a>"},{"pid":"a69d4647323bd550abd9a1af9deec9af80e38048","tid":1891542,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T02:27:46.000Z","msg":"五毛警犬做乜扮黃<br />\n照左肺未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f20af7dec7a73a9486e5c8359116a4eb7c016187","tid":1891542,"uid":52978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T02:28:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ca44251696f34e09d849cea9eddab40cf349cc6e","tid":1891542,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T02:28:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /